JFK.1991.DC.1080p.BluRay.x264-EuReKA

Details the actions of New Orleans District Attorney Jim Garrison who takes it upon himself to investigate the assassination of President John F. Kennedy in Dallas Texas in 1963. Garrison is extremely suspicious of the official story presented by the FBI and what he already knows and what he subsequently learns leads him to suspect that there is more to the story than the public is being told.
